    "title": "Negate the need for blockchain explores and full blockchain syncing for simple queries",
    "body": "Rather than download the full blockchain or a pruned version; would it be viable to peer-to-peer ask 'what is this block' or 'what is this tx'?\r\n\r\nWe download the full blockchain from several peers so why not ask peers for just on piece of info?",
